				 <h1 class="ContentTitle"><img src="images/icons/1.gif" style="margin:0px 2px -4px 0px;" alt="" class="CateIcon"/><a class="titleA" href="article/hangqing/231.html">上海期货配资：全球矿业投资增长迅猛 矿品价格涨幅波动大</a></h1>
				 <h2 class="ContentAuthor">作者:期货配资 日期:2011-11-07</h2>
			</div>
			<div id="log_231">
				<div class="Content-body">
					 <p>&nbsp;记者从6日召开的2011中国国际矿业大会上获悉，2010年全球矿业项目总投资比2009年增长21％，全球矿业已经走出低谷。与此同时，一些国家维持宽松的货币政策，流动性非常充裕，大宗商品价格仍然在高位运行<a target="_blank" style="color: rgb(0, 79, 97); font-size: 12px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-decoration: none; line-height: normal; " href="http://www.jinbenli.com/">期货配资</a>。</p>
<p style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="line-height: normal; "><span style="line-height: normal; ">Reporter</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;from 6 days of held</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;2011 China International Mining Conference</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;was informed that,</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;in 2010 the global</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;mining</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;projects with a total investment of</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;more than</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">21% growth in 2009</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">,</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;the global</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;mining industry</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;had walked out of trough</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">.</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;At the same time</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">,</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;some countries</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;maintain a loose monetary</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;policy</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">,</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;liquidity is abundant</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">,</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">commodity prices</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;still</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;moves in perch</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">.</span></p>
<div style="font-family: Arial; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; visibility: visible !important; zoom: 1 !important; filter: none; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; "><span style="line-height: normal; "><br style="line-height: normal; " />
</span></div>
<p style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;</p>
<div style="font-family: Arial; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; visibility: visible !important; zoom: 1 !important; filter: none; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;</div>
<p style="line-height: normal; ">2010年全球新登记100多个矿业投资项目，总投资额超过600亿美元；非燃料固体矿产勘查投资达到112亿美元，仅次于2008年138亿美元的记录，恢复了2009年因金融危机削减的勘查投资，预计2011年全球非燃料固体矿产勘查投资有望达到130亿－140亿美元，表明全球矿业正在回到健康发展轨道<a target="_blank" style="color: rgb(0, 79, 97); font-size: 12px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-decoration: none; line-height: normal; " href="http://www.jinbenli.com/">期货配资</a>。</p>
<p style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="line-height: normal; "><span style="line-height: normal; ">In 2010 the global</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;new registered</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;more than 100</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;mining investment projects</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">,</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;a total investment of more than</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;$60000000000</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">;</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;non fuel</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;solid mineral exploration</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">investment</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;of $11200000000</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;in 2008</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">,</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;after</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;a record $13800000000</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">,</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;restored in 2009</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;because of the financial crisis to</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;cut the</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;exploration investment</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">,</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;is expected in 2011</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;the global</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;non fuel</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;solid mineral exploration</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;investment is expected to</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;reach 13000000000</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;140</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;billion dollars</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">,</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;that the global</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;mining</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;is</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;returned to</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;the healthy development track</span><span style="line-height: normal; ">.</span></p>
<div style="font-family: Arial; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; visibility: visible !important; zoom: 1 !important; filter: none; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; "><span style="line-height: normal; "><br style="line-height: normal; " />
</span></div>
<p style="line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="line-height: normal; ">国际矿产品价格高位波动。今年1至4月原油价格快速上涨，进入5月以后大幅震荡。纽约原油期货价格由4月下旬的110美元／桶降到9月底的80美元／桶，降幅接近三成。贵金属价格呈现剧烈震荡上扬之势，金、银、铂价格超过金融危机之前的高位记录。铁矿石以及铜、铅、锌、镍等金属价格普遍上涨后逐步下调。http://space.baidu.com.cn/15000031005&nbsp;</p>
					 
